Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:29.87,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,250)\a6}製作 ？ 秋月暮葉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.67,0:01:24.70,portugal,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\a6}Vermelha 12年前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.97,0:01:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,all right！ all right！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.54,0:01:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Macaco Princeza(巨猿公主) 升起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.91,0:01:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Macaco Princeza(巨猿公主)來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.41,0:01:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把秘寶還給它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.31,0:01:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是個無法答應的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.41,0:01:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 Jesus！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.21,0:01:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是世界的終結哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.02,0:01:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒吧Kiril
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.15,0:01:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世·界·的·終·結
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.37,0:01:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界的終結哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.73,0:02:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vasili 去告訴在廣場的人換班吃飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.46,0:02:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.94,0:02:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 Jesus！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.45,0:02:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiril
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.72,0:02:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.01,0:02:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fantasma(幻影)的Kiril Capek是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.07,0:02:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！ 怎么回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.99,0:02:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫就是Kiril？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.31,0:02:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能把Monstro(怪物)人給放了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.28,0:02:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們正要搞個慶祝活動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.98,0:02:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么樣 方便的話一起參加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.66,0:02:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是哪個派系的？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.68,0:02:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Clichy派？ 或者是Satoshi派？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.44,0:02:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是Monstro的人吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.05,0:02:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.51,0:02:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是Monstro的人 不要羅嗦 你把人放了就ok
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.81,0:03:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的確討厭Monstro
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.60,0:03:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 冷戰協定我們還是遵守的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.39,0:03:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么放不放人 真是搞不懂 伙計是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝什么傻！ 胡子大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.96,0:03:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來Vermelha攝影的劇組今天光臨本店
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.34,0:03:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的Sacha這次會作為演員出道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.34,0:03:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說今天可是個可喜可賀的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.75,0:03:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起慶祝 還是打道回府 你能挑一個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學會擁有欣賞玫瑰芬芳的從容吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.12,0:04:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得的美貌真是可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.59,0:04:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭！ Kiril你在干什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.87,0:04:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許和那種女人靠得這么近！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.58,0:04:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5秒之內不離開她 我就和你分手！ 咬舌自盡！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.87,0:04:15.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.18,0:04:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你無意離開的話 4秒之內我就扣動扳機
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.50,0:04:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}愚者們的鄉愁 Part.1
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.45,0:04:32.94,portugal,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}Vermelha 三月27日
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.54,0:04:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下雨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.65,0:04:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看得見嗎？ 戴著那個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.89,0:04:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.68,0:04:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫Marisa
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.13,0:05:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Liliana關愛之家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.77,0:05:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.34,0:05:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.78,0:05:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么 Joaquin
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.73,0:05:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴！ 老太婆！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.03,0:05:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Marisa 到哪里去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.22,0:05:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還用問嗎 是好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.50,0:05:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙子！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.81,0:05:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能相信我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.88,0:05:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.76,0:05:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前也有個像你一樣的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.23,0:06:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.82,0:06:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.37,0:06:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還算吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.98,0:06:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常非常非常擔心！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.83,0:06:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里了？ 你大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.92,0:06:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 讓一讓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.11,0:06:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.22,0:06:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斗牛？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.42,0:06:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 在賭博斗牛的競技場賣東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.42,0:06:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讓大哥去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.22,0:06:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 Marco真是個好男人 我顫抖了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.22,0:06:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.49,0:06:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可是希望之星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.94,0:06:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Roman 4世都不是他對手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.41,0:06:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Roman 4世？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.57,0:06:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛中之牛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.21,0:06:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 是牛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 你聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.05,0:06:53.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論什么斗牛士對Roman 4世都是束手無策
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.30,0:06:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過Marco更加厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.70,0:06:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 討厭 電死我了 怎么辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多胡子渣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.98,0:07:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭 這個孩子剛才都害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.02,0:07:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.06,0:07:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.70,0:07:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么會！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.28,0:07:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來是為了找Satoshi
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好 Michiko現在和當年完全不一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.64,0:07:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Monstro現在已經是貨真價實的犯罪組織了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.38,0:07:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoshi是那里的老大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.02,0:07:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么事到如今去見那種家伙干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.53,0:07:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個家伙的話 應該知道Hiroshi在什么地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.87,0:07:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.82,0:07:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.75,0:07:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi絕對還活著！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.16,0:07:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也知道吧 在巴士爆炸中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是證據
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.61,0:07:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 在說什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個大咪咪晃悠悠的妹子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.12,0:07:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你對Fantasma大鬧一場之后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底出了什么事 要我告訴你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.89,0:07:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對這種事情一點興趣都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.95,0:07:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.64,0:07:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiril消失之后 你被抓了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.10,0:08:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后不久 Monstro的尸體被發現 大戰爆發
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.78,0:08:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丑話說在前頭 死了好幾個人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fantasma也好 Monstro也好 還有無關的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.11,0:08:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.65,0:08:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情都是從你開始的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.95,0:08:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為吃了虧 就把Kiril殺了 太夸張了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.47,0:08:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.28,0:08:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“我沒有殺人”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.93,0:08:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你為什么承認？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.62,0:08:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiril出門可是為了去見你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.13,0:08:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數日不歸 最后發現已經死了 不管是誰對你...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.02,0:08:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.97,0:08:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只見過一次Kiril
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.10,0:08:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連他長得什么樣 我都早忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.08,0:08:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.01,0:08:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Satoshi Batista不在這里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.66,0:08:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里只有被Monstro收編的Fantasma
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.28,0:08:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在什么地方？ Satoshi
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.89,0:08:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說一遍 這里只有Fantasma
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.55,0:09:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論你怎么說 大家都認為殺死Kiril的是Michiko 是你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了的話 請趕快離開這里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.85,0:09:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則會被殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.01,0:09:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不想再看到你的臉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.68,0:09:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 同感
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.70,0:09:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.98,0:09:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.69,0:09:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你隨意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.62,0:09:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.85,0:09:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko小姐出生的城市嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是在這里出生我不清楚 不過是在這里長大的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.02,0:09:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這里和你的老爸相識的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.69,0:10:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這里... 嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.67,0:10:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要亂動 Sacha！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.27,0:10:17.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂動的話 呯的... 一槍... 打過去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.51,0:10:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 還沒干呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.06,0:10:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法吧 給
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.70,0:10:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 就那樣 不許往這邊看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.14,0:10:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老老實實的話 我們什么都不...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等... 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.88,0:10:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.24,0:10:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.33,0:10:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 所以我叫你裝上子彈的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.74,0:12:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要隨便看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有那張
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.68,0:12:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個... 那就是那個叫Hiroshi的人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.90,0:12:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.55,0:12:27.47,portugal,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fad(250,250)}三月28日 Liliana關愛之家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.20,0:12:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.88,0:12:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里是什么地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.68,0:12:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信上寫了把你的事情拜托別人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.28,0:12:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.99,0:12:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托照顧你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.07,0:12:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進去后找一個叫Seria的大媽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.60,0:12:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都寫在上面了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.10,0:12:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡的東西 你的性格 我所知道的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.73,0:12:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么Michiko要怎么辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.51,0:12:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去找個叫Satoshi的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.48,0:13:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從小就一直和Hiroshi混在一起的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.67,0:13:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他應該知道Hiroshi的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.05,0:13:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 Hatchin 我回來接你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.18,0:13:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要去！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.96,0:13:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.65,0:13:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.28,0:13:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.25,0:13:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.33,0:13:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己能照看好自己
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.02,0:13:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礙事啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.91,0:13:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.97,0:13:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么為什么要帶著我四處亂跑!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.10,0:13:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在這種地方把我丟下!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.70,0:13:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么我要接受不認識的人的照顧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么 為什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.49,0:13:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.66,0:13:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.48,0:13:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hatchin！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:13:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 他真的還活著嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.17,0:14:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然 為什么一直放著我和Michiko小姐不管
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.74,0:14:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不相信嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.81,0:14:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.51,0:14:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連我都不相信嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.98,0:14:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.71,0:14:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么要在這里分手嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.63,0:14:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我覺得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有錢 要我怎么活下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.30,0:14:45.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vasili先生 我是Peche
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在Pinch New Street發現了Michiko Malandro
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.65,0:14:58.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一起的小孩和她分開了 現在乘著摩托向東移動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.58,0:15:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko Malandro
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.11,0:15:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你放過的那個女人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.48,0:15:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到處招搖 說Monstro如何如何的 四處搗亂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.58,0:15:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攝影組也說不想在Vermelha拍攝了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.75,0:15:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相當大的損失啊 Kiril 你要怎么辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.44,0:15:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候應該做個了斷的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.56,0:15:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事處理完之后 就請你從老大的位置上下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.26,0:15:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sacha怎么樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.53,0:15:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.62,0:15:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kiril 我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.87,0:15:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必擔心 Vasili 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.54,0:15:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護你們是我的職責
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.32,0:16:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白 Kiril
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.34,0:16:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們的職責吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.74,0:16:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看在過去的情面上 就“敗”托了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.61,0:16:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是“拜托了” 大概是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.49,0:16:25.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種水平的信可不是能拿給人看的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.22,0:16:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是丟人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.12,0:16:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒想讓她成為這樣的成年人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.19,0:16:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 那個孩子 Michiko在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.99,0:16:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才不知道去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.76,0:16:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身上有錢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.79,0:16:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好 小鬼頭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.79,0:16:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有錢就想把你丟在這里 是不是算盤打得太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.04,0:16:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這一張紙片 要我怎么辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.80,0:16:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社會哪有這么好混
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白嗎 讓她重寫 談事情在這之后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.85,0:17:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被羞辱了 不是說過不管發生什么都會保護我的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.25,0:17:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 她這么說過 那個女人！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.14,0:17:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果卻揍了我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.58,0:17:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原諒！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.78,0:17:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要揍她 我也要揍她！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.20,0:17:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就知道耍帥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.55,0:17:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么“礙事啊！”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.48,0:17:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明已經眼眶濕潤了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 其實她很孤獨 只是在逞強
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這些事情 首先我要揍她
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對要揍她！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.17,0:17:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,談事情在這之后！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.47,0:17:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了救被Fantasma抓住的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.06,0:18:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算去抓Kiril Capek的女人做人質
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.05,0:18:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果錯找到我 是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.92,0:18:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么說 那個女人是好女人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.11,0:18:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要一個人去嗎？ 那種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.44,0:18:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不害怕嗎？ 說不定會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.04,0:18:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會死嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我一個人的死能讓大家得救的話 也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.14,0:18:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我自作主張的 只有我自己一個人去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.35,0:18:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 不如放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.86,0:18:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨停了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.27,0:19:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不餓嗎？ 吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.06,0:19:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我陪你一起去 Kiril那里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.90,0:19:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那樣的 Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.64,0:19:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個家伙是膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.86,0:19:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以必須去找他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.27,0:19:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不去找到他... 是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.64,0:19:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 你也存了不少錢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.56,0:19:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 攢錢攢錢 已經超越了拼命的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.74,0:19:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的錢用在什么地方 大家都在議論
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.19,0:19:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還用問 都是為了自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.74,0:19:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老后誰會來照看我啊 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.26,0:19:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近我的老腰老腿明顯不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.70,0:19:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷心落淚的時候也是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.71,0:20:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是還有孩子們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.52,0:20:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都不會在意我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.84,0:20:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子們離開之后就沒有消息了 誰也不會在意我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.24,0:20:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我本來就討厭小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.33,0:20:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廢話多 臟兮兮 自以為是 非常討厭！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.88,0:20:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個家伙是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.48,0:20:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一邊也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.12,0:20:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.01,0:20:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這個小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.70,0:20:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個和Michiko在一起的小鬼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.10,0:20:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 把她帶回來
